Hi all,<br><br>
I would be remiss if I didn't reply to all of the wonderful messages that were directed my way in the last 2 days.<br><br>
It is safe to say that each person who enters any kind of website, chat room or what-have-you, has a basic desire or need to be accepted. All of us can agree on that, right?<br><br>
Yesterday was very special for me. Finally, there was a realization that even if our opinions are different, there is still room for friendship. All of your posts meant alot to me.<br><br>
Lo and behold, there are several *new posters* who have decided to get their feet wet! I want to encourage you guys to keep writing. There is an old war horse in cyberspace who often says, &quot;Say what you mean, and mean what you say.&quot; Things can get a bit treacherous around here, but I have always thought that the best thing to do is to hang in there. This is a pretty good bunch.<br><br>
I will post more very soon, but would like to read some of the newer guys stuff for a while. Just a bit tired, but very well pleased.<br><br>
Peace to all,<br><br>
Tom<br><br>

